},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:11:58.000Z","msg":"如果同時上訴定罪及判刑，上訴庭可以加刑<br />\n<br />\n如果只就定罪上訴，就不可以<br />\n<br />\n但就算被告只上訴定罪，律政師都可以申請cross appeal 佢判刑"},{"pid":"98c3803dbe2029a93862704e87319748e4420379","tid":771993,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母閪斷正就咪撚搞咁柒多嘢啦"},{"pid":"f540f7fcb653a5261e30dddad039b041c5bc3b1e","tid":771993,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c49bfd96734b00e75f26ca061ac71aa985129c","tid":771993,"uid":121785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3ab3204216790a21b3924605f853d99fa271410","tid":771993,"uid":36321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:15:11.000Z","msg":"上訴庭多數打得甩<br />\n唔好唔記得上訴庭個三個主官係咩底先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:04:22.000Z","msg":"應該上原訟庭唔係上訴庭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"因為原判係裁判署，所以上訴就會去原訟庭，一個官審"}]}